  ('2026-04-01'::date, 3, 'The LORD is close to the brokenhearted and saves those who are crushed in spirit.'),
  ('2026-04-02'::date, 3, 'For I am the LORD your God who takes hold of your right hand and says to you, Do not fear; I will help you.'),
  ('2026-04-03'::date, 3, 'But blessed is the one who trusts in the LORD, whose confidence is in him.'),
  ('2026-04-04'::date, 3, 'Therefore do not worry about tomorrow, for tomorrow will worry about itself. Each day has enough trouble of its own.'),
  ('2026-04-05'::date, 3, 'I have told you these things, so that in me you may have peace. In this world you will have trouble. But take heart! I have overcome the world.'),
  ('2026-04-06'::date, 3, 'Therefore, there is now no condemnation for those who are in Christ Jesus.'),
  ('2026-04-07'::date, 3, 'Praise be to the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Father of compassion and the God of all comfort, who comforts us in all our troubles, so that we can comfort those in any trouble with the comfort we ourselves receive from God.'),
  ('2026-04-08'::date, 3, 'Let us not become weary in doing good, for at the proper time we will reap a harvest if we do not give up.'),
  ('2026-04-09'::date, 3, 'Let us then approach God’s throne of grace with confidence, so that we may receive mercy and find grace to help us in our time of need.'),
  ('2026-04-10'::date, 3, 'But you are a chosen people, a royal priesthood, a holy nation, God’s special possession, that you may declare the praises of him who called you out of darkness into his wonderful light.'),
  ('2026-04-11'::date, 3, 'But he said to me, "My grace is sufficient for you, for my power is made perfect in weakness." Therefore I will boast all the more gladly about my weaknesses, so that Christ’s power may rest on me.'),
